cucumber-jvm-maven is a project for testing command line application for converting Roman Numerals to numbers.
As testing framework cucumber-jvm is used.


 Prerequisites :    
    Java JDK should be installed (version 1.5 or above )
    Maven latest build should be downloaded and installed 
    (see http://maven.apache.org/download.html for instruction)

  To run test:
    Download the project
    From command prompt change directory to cucumber-jvm-maven (where pom.xml file is located)
    execute command: mvn test
    Also you can run test from Eclipse IDE : Run As -> Maven test

    test results you can see in folder: ...cucumber-jvm-maven\target\surefire-reports

